{
  "id": "adv_main_04_04_02",
  "title": "星空編1章17話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはフェスに参加しないんだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE won't be participating in the festival…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君が誘ってみたけど\n活動休止期間中だからって断られたそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san invited them‚\nbut they apparently declined‚ saying they were on hiatus",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "活動休止なんて余程の覚悟がないと言い出せないわ\nそれだけに、軽々しく覆す訳にはいかないでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't just say you're going on hiatus unless you're really prepared\nThat's why they can't just overturn it so easily",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね……。トリエルが高く羽ばたくためにって\n活動休止を決めた瑠依ちゃんの覚悟は本物だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…. Rui-chan's decision to stop activities so that\nTRINITYAiLE could fly high was genuine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それは瑠依ちゃん達が沢山悩んで決めたことだから\n尊重しなきゃって思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is something Rui-chan's group thought a lot about and decided on‚\nso I think we should respect it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、星見プロのお祭りなのに\nトリエルの三人がいないのはやっぱり寂しいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ it's a Hoshimi Prods. festival‚\nit's a so sad that the three of TRINITYAiLE isn't there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの活動休止っていつまで続くのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How long TRINITYAiLE's hiatus will last?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5554650943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依の性格だと、何かを掴めたと確信するまでは\n戻って来ないかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Given Rui's personality‚ she might not return until she's convinced\nshe's achieved something",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 62.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "それって、何も掴めなかったら\nこのまま星見プロを辞めるのもありえるってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does that mean she could quit Hoshimi Prods.\nif she doesn't achieve anything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルが星見プロを辞めるなんて……\nそんなこと、絶対ない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE quitting Hoshimi Prods.…\nAbsolutely‚ not…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思いたいけど、あの感じだと\n絶対にないとは言い切れないかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to think so‚ but if that's the feeling‚\nI can't say for sure it doesn't happen",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが月ストを脱退した時みたいに\n星見プロを離れることが成長に繋がると思ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Kotono-chan thought that leaving Hoshimi Prods.\nwould lead to her growth like when she left Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "ストイックな瑠依ちゃんなら、 全てを捨てて\n強くなる道を選ぶかもしれないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then stoic Rui-chan might choose to give up everything\nand become stronger",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "強くなるために……勝つために、全てを捨てる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To become strong… to win‚ give up everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4832193693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "もしもそうなったら、きっと優とすみれは\n瑠依について行くでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that were to happen‚ I'm sure Yu and Sumire\nwould follow Rui",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.333333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "（私達はトリエルの分まで頑張るって決めたけど……）\n（もし本当に、このまま戻って来なかったら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We decided to do our best for TRINITYAiLE…）\n（If‚ really‚ she don't come back like this…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.733333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1141717117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 117.5237834454
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 117.6275050641
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……\nはぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…\nSigh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.733333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらがため息なんてめずらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's rare to see Sakura sighing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.287443177,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 145.89066499999603,
          "startTime": 122.433333842
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、莉央ちゃん！？　どうしてここに？\nいつ日本に戻って来たの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Rio-chan!? Why are you here?\nWhen did you come back to Japan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "今日帰国して、ついさっき寮に着いたところよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I returned to Japan today and just arrived at the dorm",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4044952076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと私と芽衣で\n空港まで迎えに行ってきたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ Mei‚ and I\nwent to the airport to pick up",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2571369649,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 288.8386088999937,
          "startTime": 135.6000005086
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん！\n……そうだったんだね。莉央ちゃん、おかえりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan!\n…I see. Rio-chan‚ welcome back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ただいま\n……どうしたの、さくら。何か悩み事？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm back\n…What's up‚ Sakura. Are you worried about something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、トリエルのことで……このまま瑠依ちゃん達が\n戻って来ないこともありえるのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's about TRINITYAiLE… I'm worried that Rui-chan's group\nmight not come back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを考えたら、不安になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about that‚ makes me anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2990304948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それは余計な心配ね\n瑠依は星見プロを辞めたりしないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's unnecessary worry\nRui won't quit Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそう言い切れるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can you be sure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3835430305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 173.8404364347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルと同じように、私達も日本での活動を休止して\nアメリカに渡ったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like TRINITYAiLE‚ we took a break from our activities in Japan\nand moved to the America",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.833333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、休止中に星見プロを辞めようとは\n微塵も思わなかった。どうしてだか分かる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But during our hiatus‚ we never considered\nquitting Hoshimi Prods. Do you know why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.933333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "この場所が好きだからよ\n三枝さんに{user}さん、さとみさん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because we love this place\nSaegusa-san‚ {user}-san‚ Satomi-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、競い合う仲間でありライバル達……みんなが\n集うこの場所が――星見プロが気に入っているの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And our friends and rivals… this place\nwhere we all gather―― Hoshimi Prods. is what we love",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_04_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロは私達の居場所なの。だから私達もトリエルも\n辞めようなんて思わないわ。絶対にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Prods. is where we belong. So neither we nor TRINITYAiLE\nwould think of quitting. Never",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
