      "text": "……その感覚、分かります。私も月ストに復帰した時\n帰って来たんだ、って実感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand that feeling. When I returned to Moon Tempest‚\nI also felt like I was back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.6999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
