      "text": "きっとそれは瑠依さん達も同じだから……\n私達もトリエルの力になりたいと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure that's the same for Rui-san's group…\nWe wanted to help TRINITYAiLE‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.4999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 229.5333307919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
