      "text": "その時はもちろん、私達も力を貸すわよ\n瑠依達はバンプロ時代からの後輩だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we will help you then too\nRui's group is my junior from our Van Prods. days…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.5999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
