      "text": "勝つために頑張るのは悪いことじゃない……\n実際、さくらちゃんの影響で最近のサニピは絶好調……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not a bad thing to work hard to win…\nIn fact‚ Sunny Peace has been doing really well lately thanks to Sakura-chan's influence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.8666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
