      "text": "だからみんなで話して、今はさくらちゃんを信じよう\n一緒に頑張ろうって……そういう結論になったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we all talked about it and decided to believe in Sakura for now\nand work hard together… That's the conclusion we came to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.9667007447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
